text:
Corona Ave. (tracks thereon) west side, at and adjoining Otis Ave. Views 2, 3 and 4, show rear views of the J.H. Smith Shady Lake farmhouse. (small delivery truck in rear thereof). View No. 1 shows the tree that stood in the rear of the house. See views located as Corona Ave., west side, opposite Fifty-fourth Ave. for more data.

Oct. 1928.
Views 2 & 3 : Feb. 1925
View 4 : May 1926

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
